%h4
  Birthdays This Week
- unless @birthday_clients.blank?
  - @birthday_clients.each do |birthday_client|
    %p= birthday_client.name + " - " + birthday_client.birthday.change(:year => Date.today.year).strftime("%A %B #{birthday_client.birthday.day.ordinalize}")
- else
  Zilch, zip, nada

